Timber products: Production, imports, exports, and new supply of lumber in the United States, specified years, 1799-1958

Dataset containing statistics for timber products. All units are in Million Board Ft, unless otherwise specified. All vectors are numeric.

piet_all

Format

A data frame with 58 observations on 23 variables:

Years

Years

Prod.Tot

Production Total

Prod.SW

Production of Softwoods

Prod.HW

Production of Hardwoods

Imports.Tot

Total Imports

Imports.SW

Imports for Softwood

Imports.HW

Imports for Hardwoods

Imports.Mixed

Imports for Mixed Woods

Imports.Mixed.PercOfTot

Mixed Woods Percent of Total Imports

Imports.SW.PercOfTot

Softwoods Percent of Total Imports

Imports.HW.PercOfTot

Hardwoods Percent of Total Imports

Imports.Estimated.SW

Estimated Softwood Imports

Imports.Estimated.HW

Estimated Hardwood Imports

Exports.Tot

Total Exports

Exports.SW

Softwood Exports

Exports.HW

Hardwood Exports

Exports.Mixed

Mixed Woods Exports

Exports.Mixed.PercOfTot

Mixed Woods Percent of Total Exports

Exports.SW.PercOfTot

Softwoods Percent of Total Exports

Exports.HW.PercOfTot

Hardwoods Percent of Total Exports

Exports.Estimated.SW

Estimated Softwood Exports

Exports.Estimated.HW

Estimated Hardwood Exports

NewSupply

New Supply

PerCapita

Per Capita Use, in Board ft.

Source

USFS Estimations and Bureau of Census Data
